snippet.textDisplay: I really like the whole "Team 9" thing they have going.  Like a reserve of fresh meat for the grinder, ready to go, should any of the 8 teams lose a player or players.  Even if you don't make one of the 8 teams cuts you go straight to "Team 9" & still have a chance to play.  Would LOVE to see Tebow play btw.
